title: Act 3 rewards not registering....
body:
http://i.imgur.com/Rwo3q1k.jpg

It updated my wins with new items but not my overall wins....and it's definitely been at least two minutes after my win....

replies.body:
Hey Squishy. 

You have to finish these objectives in order. So after you get two wins with Bilgewater items, your next set of objectives will begin to be counted.
